n希望zack snyder 無人制肘既情況下拍得出dawn of the dead 既水準"},{"pid":"09f9a29d7813e89079d54a842984af0e22bf52ac","tid":1078843,"uid":125477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T23:45:56.000Z","msg":"Wrong turn<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35051a4ba763571a2fecdab756fcb030d6c097ff","tid":1078843,"uid":10998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T23:57:02.000Z","msg":"笑死人凶間"},{"pid":"b35e2e3684d0bb7e03a00a6f3cc4bddc67382e58","tid":1078843,"uid":134945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T23:57:35.000Z","msg":"The strain"},{"pid":"69b63b034f403aa5ed6c05dd8b9e927819d96263","tid":1078843,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:13:13.000Z","msg":"笑死人凶間"},{"pid":"fa4519dda5c29d2002638c4596568caf990710df","tid":1078843,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:30:44.000Z","msg":"Deadsnow1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nWar world z"},{"pid":"37c31591ec8745cdcc6391ff6a3bd6f3d559365f","tid":1078843,"uid":115294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:38:49.000Z","msg":"無人講我依兩套 <br />\n慘慘豬<br />\n<br />\nZombieland <br />\n<br />\nDust till dawn (唔記得第1/2集最好睇-其他係廢既）"},{"pid":"e843ee6ebe4d82ce9de414cd6d03192e017de25f","tid":1078843,"uid":219732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e98d2311c86702b61ed656bb9deedfeb30eab5e","tid":1078843,"uid":4377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e2f22a5926f95b40dd48e6cf6a5e51d88ed0e18e","tid":1078843,"uid":219732,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T14:35:46.000Z","msg":"Warm bodies"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T15:50:35.000Z","msg":"每年都重溫一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:38:31.000Z","msg":"Everybody's got a hungry heart ~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/lom